// ============================================================================
// ZigZag Corridors (ZZC)
// Version: 1.0
// Author: WavesUnchained
// Build: 2025-10-11 20:19:00
// ============================================================================
// Advanced ZigZag indicator with Keltner/Donchian Channels and BB/KC Squeeze detection
//
// Features:
//   ✓ Non-repainting ZigZag with ATR/Percent/Deviation modes
//   ✓ Keltner Channel - Adaptive volatility envelope
//   ✓ Donchian Channel - Objective range detection
//   ✓ BB/KC Squeeze Detection - Compression/Expansion timing
//   ✓ Corridor Logic - Interesting zones between channels
//   ✓ Sliding Window Flow (SWF) - Fair value window + state machine
//   ✓ AVWAP Reset - Anchored VWAP shifts with ZigZag legs
//   ✓ Flow States - Expansion/Pullback/Continuation/Reversal detection
//   ✓ ARRA Rebuild Zones - Action/Reaction-Analysis with quality gate
//   ✓ Last-Leg Fibonacci - Horizontal 38.2%/50%/61.8% retracements
//   ✓ CPM Signal Engine - Mode-based adaptive thresholds (Strong/Moderate/Loose)
//   ✓ Bidirectional Scoring - Separate bull/bear composite scores
//   ✓ Divergence Boost - Threshold relaxation on confirmed divergence
//   ✓ Diamond Gating - Pivot-confirmed exhaustion zone filtering
//   ✓ RZ Proximity Boost - Enhanced signals near reversal zones
//   ✓ Repainting Protection - HTF confirmation in Strong mode
//   ✓ Signal Strength Classification - Strong/Moderate/Weak quality levels
//   ✓ Live Leg Info Table - Real-time statistics
//   ✓ Smart Alerts - Zone touches and squeeze breaks
//   ✓ Customizable Visualization - Colors, labels, fills
//
// Indicators Used:
//   • ZigZag (ATR/Percent/Deviation based)
//   • Keltner Channels (EMA + ATR)
//   • Donchian Channels (Highest/Lowest)
//   • Bollinger Bands (for squeeze detection)
//   • ATR (Average True Range)
//   • EMA (Exponential Moving Average)
//
// ============================================================================

//@version=6
strategy("ZigZag Corridors (ZZC) [WavesUnchained] [STRATEGY]",
         overlay=true, 
         max_labels_count=500, 
         max_lines_count=500)


